title: Henrietta
description:
![3DF340AC-7401-4A7B-8F9F-15F0C038D70A](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3238096/160026691-c29e3b05-964d-43e7-9368-d2a1ac73bbcc.jpeg)

> Henrietta is a revival of a font by the same name that was (probably) designed in the 1980s. It’s a Souvenir rip-off. But a rip-off with its own underlying logic.

I already love where Henrietta is at in v0.1, I can’t wait to see what’s in store.
